title: The Shawshank Redemption
description: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption through acts of common decency.

title: Fe
description: The Player Stratocaster HSS Floyd MN TPLcombines noble optics with classy equipment. The alder body is painted in classic Tide Pool, the maple neck is dressed in a comfortable modern C profile. An Alnico HSS pickup set provides versatile sound. The Player Strat Floyd can also score in terms of hardware: a Floyd Rose tremolo ensures high tuning stability.
